{
  "storylets": [
    {
      "id": "order_scout_ranger_t7",
      "title": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_title}Ride alone",
      "setup": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_setup}Your lord does not call a rider. He calls you by name and points past the ridge. He has come to trust your eye for country. No second man, no sergeant — just the horse, the bow on your knee, and what you can bring back.",
      "theme": "duty",
      "category": "named_order",
      "severity": "normal",
      "scope": {
        "context": "any",
        "slots": {
          "lord": { "role": "enlisted_lord" }
        }
      },
      "trigger": ["is_enlisted", "rank_gte:7", "flag:committed_path_ranger"],
      "class_affinity": {
        "Cavalry": 1.5,
        "HorseArcher": 1.6,
        "Ranged": 1.2
      },
      "arc": {
        "duration_hours": 10,
        "phases": [
          {
            "id": "scout_ranger_t7_mid",
            "duration_hours": 8,
            "pool_prefix": "order_scout_ranger_t7_mid_",
            "fire_interval_hours": 2,
            "delivery": "auto"
          },
          {
            "id": "scout_ranger_t7_resolve",
            "duration_hours": 2,
            "pool_prefix": "order_scout_ranger_t7_resolve_",
            "fire_interval_hours": 0,
            "delivery": "auto"
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "accept_diligent",
          "text": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_accept_diligent_text}Ride wide. Bring the map back clean.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_accept_diligent_tt}Start solo scout arc. Diligent.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "start_arc", "intent": "diligent" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "decline",
          "text": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_decline_text}Beg off. The country is thick today.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_decline_tt}Decline. Relation + scrutiny hit.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "relation_change", "target_slot": "lord", "delta": -2 },
            { "apply": "scrutiny_up_small" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "order_scout_ranger_t7_mid_vigil",
      "title": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_mid_vigil_title}A long still hour",
      "setup": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_mid_vigil_setup}You sit the horse in a clump of alder and watch a valley for an hour without moving. The country tells you what it holds when you give it time. A thin line of smoke bends east — woodcutters, not soldiers. You mark it anyway.",
      "theme": "duty",
      "category": "named_order",
      "severity": "normal",
      "cooldown_days": 2,
      "intent_affinity": { "diligent": 1.4 },
      "scope": { "context": "any" },
      "trigger": ["is_enlisted"],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "main",
          "text": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_mid_vigil_main_text}Stay in cover. Watch until the hour turns.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_mid_vigil_main_tt}Scouting XP.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "skill_xp", "skill": "Scouting", "amount": 25 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "order_scout_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent",
      "title": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_title}A clean account",
      "setup": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_setup}You ride in at dusk alone, as sent. Your lord reads the map without a word and folds it into his coat. He says only that he will send you again. For a ranger, that is the praise.",
      "theme": "duty",
      "category": "named_order",
      "severity": "normal",
      "scope": {
        "context": "any",
        "slots": {
          "lord": { "role": "enlisted_lord" }
        }
      },
      "trigger": ["is_enlisted"],
      "intent_affinity": { "diligent": 2.0 },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "close",
          "text": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_close_text}Unsaddle. Water the horse.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_scout_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_close_tt}Rank XP + Scouting + relation.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "rank_xp_minor" },
            { "apply": "skill_xp", "skill": "Scouting", "amount": 40 },
            { "apply": "lord_relation_up_small" },
            { "apply": "clear_active_named_order" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "order_escort_ranger_t7",
      "title": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_title}Ride outside the column",
      "setup": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_setup}A diplomat's wagon needs a screen on the flanks, not a guard on the tailboard. Your lord sends you to range wide of the road — eyes on the country, not on the coach. You know this kind of work.",
      "theme": "duty",
      "category": "named_order",
      "severity": "normal",
      "scope": {
        "context": "any",
        "slots": {
          "lord": { "role": "enlisted_lord" }
        }
      },
      "trigger": ["is_enlisted", "rank_gte:7", "flag:committed_path_ranger"],
      "class_affinity": {
        "Cavalry": 1.4,
        "HorseArcher": 1.5,
        "Ranged": 1.2
      },
      "arc": {
        "duration_hours": 10,
        "phases": [
          {
            "id": "escort_ranger_t7_mid",
            "duration_hours": 8,
            "pool_prefix": "order_escort_ranger_t7_mid_",
            "fire_interval_hours": 2,
            "delivery": "auto"
          },
          {
            "id": "escort_ranger_t7_resolve",
            "duration_hours": 2,
            "pool_prefix": "order_escort_ranger_t7_resolve_",
            "fire_interval_hours": 0,
            "delivery": "auto"
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "accept_diligent",
          "text": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_accept_diligent_text}Out to the flanks. Eyes on the brush.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_accept_diligent_tt}Start flanking-escort arc. Diligent.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "start_arc", "intent": "diligent" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "decline",
          "text": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_decline_text}Beg off. Let another ride wide.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_decline_tt}Decline. Relation + scrutiny hit.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "relation_change", "target_slot": "lord", "delta": -2 },
            { "apply": "scrutiny_up_small" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "order_escort_ranger_t7_mid_road",
      "title": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_mid_road_title}Tracks off the road",
      "setup": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_mid_road_setup}Two sets of unshod hooves cross the track and turn into the pine. Fresh. You can bring the wagon to a halt and bear the trail alone, or fall back to the column and report.",
      "theme": "duty",
      "category": "named_order",
      "severity": "elevated",
      "cooldown_days": 2,
      "intent_affinity": { "diligent": 1.4 },
      "scope": { "context": "any" },
      "trigger": ["is_enlisted"],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "main",
          "text": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_mid_road_main_text}Bear the trail. Quiet and wide.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_mid_road_main_tt}Scouting XP.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "skill_xp", "skill": "Scouting", "amount": 25 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "order_escort_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent",
      "title": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_title}No trouble on the road",
      "setup": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_setup}The wagon rolls into camp without a scratch because nothing touched it. You rode the country, not the wheels. The merchant never saw you. Your lord knows.",
      "theme": "duty",
      "category": "named_order",
      "severity": "normal",
      "scope": {
        "context": "any",
        "slots": {
          "lord": { "role": "enlisted_lord" }
        }
      },
      "trigger": ["is_enlisted"],
      "intent_affinity": { "diligent": 2.0 },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "close",
          "text": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_close_text}Hand the reins off. Walk the line.",
          "tooltip": "{=order_escort_ranger_t7_resolve_diligent_close_tt}Rank XP + Scouting + relation.",
          "effects": [
            { "apply": "rank_xp_minor" },
            { "apply": "skill_xp", "skill": "Scouting", "amount": 40 },
            { "apply": "lord_relation_up_small" },
            { "apply": "clear_active_named_order" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
